OL,3,CReform to accept donations in Bitcoin,
OL,4,CFarage says
OL,6,FReform UK are now accepting donations
OL,7,Fin Bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies,
OL,8,FNigel Farage has announced.
OL,10,FThe party leader told the Bitcoin
OL,11,FConference in Las Vegas he would
OL,12,F"launch in Britain a crypto
OL,13,Frevolution" and make London "one of
OL,14,Fthe major trading centres of the
OL,15,Fworld".
OL,17,FThe plans are part of Reform's Crypto
OL,18,FAssets and Digital Finance Bill, which
OL,19,Fthey would put into effect if they won
OL,20,Fthe next general election.
